				<h1>Meet <span style="color: #ff66cc;">Lyla</span>.</h1>
				<p>She's unable to use her back legs, but she gets around pretty well with the help of her doggie wheelchair. Lyla has found her home in the loving arms of Ruff Love Rescue founder, Sue Rogers.</p>
				<a class="button" href="adopt/">Meet her friends</a>
