					<a href="adopt/">
						<h3>Adopt</h3>
						<img src="images/featured/adopt.JPG" class="img-responsive">
					</a>
					We have lots of dogs that are looking for forever homes, and we regularly take in new dogs who are in need of our help. We'll do everything we can to help you find your perfect match among the many different dogs that are in our care.
				</div> 
				<div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 blocks">
					<a href="foster/">
						<h3>Foster</h3>
						<img src="images/featured/foster.JPG" class="img-responsive">
					</a>
					If you're not ready to make a full commitment, but want to help homless dogs, you can become a foster parent. Fostering is an extrememly rewarding experience that will also save the life of a dog that might not otherwise be saved.
				</div> 
				<div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 blocks">
					<a href="donate/">
						<h3>Donate</h3>
						<img src="images/featured/donate.jpg" class="img-responsive">
					</a>
					As a non-profit, fund raising is one of Ruff Love's biggest challenges. Without your help, Ruff Love Rescue would not be able to support our many programs. Even a little bit helps. <a href="http://news.petmeds.com/">PetMeds</a> graciously donates to Ruff Love Rescue.
				</div> 
